{"id": "ChIJdUd4uN2Tj4ARh21YAJWogxA", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 218, "displayName": {"text": "Always Yours Bakery Cafe", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJdUd4uN2Tj4ARh21YAJWogxA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Nd1owMHdVVnA1U2tWVmEzRldRMnR0WXkxWGFIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My favorite bakery and cafe in Castro Valley! The macarons, cheesecakes, fruit tarts, and more are all great but my favorite are their cream puffs, especially the character ones. They also have drinks - the boba is not too soft, and their fruit teas are also good! Their matcha series is really popular and tasty as well, and I like how you can adjust the sweetness.\n\nI've followed them since they opened in 2021 and the owner, Natalie, is very responsive to feedback. I appreciate how invested she and her team are in keeping this place a local gem!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My favorite bakery and cafe in Castro Valley! The macarons, cheesecakes, fruit tarts, and more are all great but my favorite are their cream puffs, especially the character ones. They also have drinks - the boba is not too soft, and their fruit teas are also good! Their matcha series is really popular and tasty as well, and I like how you can adjust the sweetness.\n\nI've followed them since they opened in 2021 and the owner, Natalie, is very responsive to feedback. I appreciate how invested she and her team are in keeping this place a local gem!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kelly G", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100004311220894013933/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6X03jME-kCRS4HZFgI_Ap0xp_rY2vbuApZDcGxgRRMEnUVkmKMQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-18T05:04:54.953429161Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Nd1owMHdVVnA1U2tWVmEzRldRMnR0WXkxWGFIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Nd1owMHdVVnA1U2tWVmEzRldRMnR0WXkxWGFIYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f93ddb8784775:0x1083a89500586d87"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdUd4uN2Tj4ARh21YAJWogxA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kM05UUkVlRFZxYnpFM1EwSlNjRkZRWTB4MVZsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Their Matcha Lattes are the best!  They use Jade Leaf ceremonial grade matcha from Japan. My favorite 3 are Banana pudding, guava and strawberries Matcha. One of these drinks and a UBE cookie and I am set!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Their Matcha Lattes are the best!  They use Jade Leaf ceremonial grade matcha from Japan. My favorite 3 are Banana pudding, guava and strawberries Matcha. One of these drinks and a UBE cookie and I am set!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Julie", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110064559045406350744/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSjPSh7oqKRfbg6J5e24r-sjs393Bf1Skkbo2NifMu08U6dmc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-14T17:30:05.334521800Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kM05UUkVlRFZxYnpFM1EwSlNjRkZRWTB4MVZsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kM05UUkVlRFZxYnpFM1EwSlNjRkZRWTB4MVZsRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f93ddb8784775:0x1083a89500586d87"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdUd4uN2Tj4ARh21YAJWogxA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5VFF5MTVWazR5YmpKNFF6ZExjRFF3TUdWMFRrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very nice place to come sit and enjoy a few cookies and a drink.\nI personally got and enjoyed the Ube Crinkle Cookie. A very soft center crunchy edges and a sweet buttery flavor making it a very delicious purchase.\nAlso enjoyed a Tiramisu Cup.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very nice place to come sit and enjoy a few cookies and a drink.\nI personally got and enjoyed the Ube Crinkle Cookie. A very soft center crunchy edges and a sweet buttery flavor making it a very delicious purchase.\nAlso enjoyed a Tiramisu Cup.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Vicky T", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100125154509720114221/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUp6HS_5lGtvLJmDzu38ZZKRbHeZ7oaOKZZ2XsLpt0MxmsJ6yqTRA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-28T02:29:48.556426241Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5VFF5MTVWazR5YmpKNFF6ZExjRFF3TUdWMFRrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5VFF5MTVWazR5YmpKNFF6ZExjRFF3TUdWMFRrRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f93ddb8784775:0x1083a89500586d87"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdUd4uN2Tj4ARh21YAJWogxA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tnMVdVUk5iV3BKV1dGMFNXRkNRbWxyWm1wb2QyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "10 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We catered Always Yours for our special day, and we're ecstatic to say that we made the grand slam choice from all our dessert tastings.\n\nWe received countless compliments from our guests on how delightful the dessert bar was. Natalie designed and brought us a dazzling display. The Asian-inspired flavors were immaculate, the macaroons were incredibly fresh and crispy (in-store variants may not do them justice), and cake buttercream was light and fluffy. Each guest had around 1.25 servings each.\n\nWe can't wait to work with Always Yours again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We catered Always Yours for our special day, and we're ecstatic to say that we made the grand slam choice from all our dessert tastings.\n\nWe received countless compliments from our guests on how delightful the dessert bar was. Natalie designed and brought us a dazzling display. The Asian-inspired flavors were immaculate, the macaroons were incredibly fresh and crispy (in-store variants may not do them justice), and cake buttercream was light and fluffy. Each guest had around 1.25 servings each.\n\nWe can't wait to work with Always Yours again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rick Huang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100603738465811075496/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCEOAosD_qDe7dJecFwdFaGqWMpX2xsRdfEBie4vSaOmK4VD8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-21T10:16:15.915364064Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tnMVdVUk5iV3BKV1dGMFNXRkNRbWxyWm1wb2QyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tnMVdVUk5iV3BKV1dGMFNXRkNRbWxyWm1wb2QyYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f93ddb8784775:0x1083a89500586d87"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdUd4uN2Tj4ARh21YAJWogxA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WRlRFd3RibFpmY0U1TmJHdFRWeTFPUVdVelNHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The hype is real! 4.5 **** rounded up to 5 ***** for me.\n\n\"Treat Yo Self!\"\n...says the ad outside.\n\n...and treat myself I did! Stopped by to satisfy those Sweet Tooth cravings when the Gods of Sugar called...\n\nbased on the stellar ratings of course... ( *  - )\n\nCute little cafe in the Castro Valley Shopping Center. Not a lot of seating inside, I think there is more seating outside. Bright and inviting decor, friendly staff and some brilliant desserts. There are a few discounts for Veterans and Yelp Check ins, so be sure to look physically around the store for promotions. I only say the signs after I already ordered.\n\n#SweetTooth:\n~ Mango Japanese Souffle Cheesecake - 5/5\nExactly as described! A Souffle Cheesecake! Excellent texture; part Souffle and part Cheesecake! Typical Asian praise: Not too sweet! lol. Brilliant Mango flavor, very well balanced, not too strong, not too heavy either.\n\nsignature drinks:\n~ earl gray crème brûlée - 5/5\nWow! Honestly, I didn't expect this to be that good! While it is slightly on the sweeter side, it's absolutely brilliant! Good Earl Gray flavor with that  rich custard base of crème brûlée mixed in with bits of caramelized sugar. DELISH!! Be sure to mix this your drink before digging into it, the flavors are in layers.\n\nI'll be back when I'm in the area...", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The hype is real! 4.5 **** rounded up to 5 ***** for me.\n\n\"Treat Yo Self!\"\n...says the ad outside.\n\n...and treat myself I did! Stopped by to satisfy those Sweet Tooth cravings when the Gods of Sugar called...\n\nbased on the stellar ratings of course... ( *  - )\n\nCute little cafe in the Castro Valley Shopping Center. Not a lot of seating inside, I think there is more seating outside. Bright and inviting decor, friendly staff and some brilliant desserts. There are a few discounts for Veterans and Yelp Check ins, so be sure to look physically around the store for promotions. I only say the signs after I already ordered.\n\n#SweetTooth:\n~ Mango Japanese Souffle Cheesecake - 5/5\nExactly as described! A Souffle Cheesecake! Excellent texture; part Souffle and part Cheesecake! Typical Asian praise: Not too sweet! lol. Brilliant Mango flavor, very well balanced, not too strong, not too heavy either.\n\nsignature drinks:\n~ earl gray crème brûlée - 5/5\nWow! Honestly, I didn't expect this to be that good! While it is slightly on the sweeter side, it's absolutely brilliant! Good Earl Gray flavor with that  rich custard base of crème brûlée mixed in with bits of caramelized sugar. DELISH!! Be sure to mix this your drink before digging into it, the flavors are in layers.\n\nI'll be back when I'm in the area...", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mika'ele Keni'", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101914927410313536501/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2l7T0oG0_YMsHJ7t_vzLlDE0tXhVKzvLL58ibTnzAw-bMBc3-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2025-06-23T16:20:34.259299606Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WRlRFd3RibFpmY0U1TmJHdFRWeTFPUVdVelNHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WRlRFd3RibFpmY0U1TmJHdFRWeTFPUVdVelNHYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f93ddb8784775:0x1083a89500586d87"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJdUd4uN2Tj4ARh21YAJWogxA/photos/AWCwydhJ63k8dpFC3VsVyKXG0Sh3RnQHZ4leOr6KX0Pc36_ow0LOc-sKstRr0OFN-xtI8cSpTSqkOMejeHbr5b7XYdTn-jEQqHwnX0tIGbLhmR9D-Q-qGC_YLMYwcLeJK8IYFfLhovoyTn5CFZB2RsiAz1eGVuamAEcvs_WkJNWluWVyvpwKEyU3v-ReJ8K31GTc0LRZtZ7KN0VPxooVCzRvuUDKo7z6z6ApxGBbzt40l5vQ2IVYpMPX35obHNcEgskh8wNTk6iNApWximQeXU2Qdn3TFJ3uS3YVVcGqqacfvBXRwRQxOJX-GSrM0yI6epSCMn_56fHmioQg3vNdCrHIZVQzJ4WL_kcrmNB3jYcpPcWWYH2_AFeCdb5HWcKU7lScv7_tyFjIkdMZ_jqExkfHPoS8LTZrk3CTWHYfw9M4mbZALIVzeO1icK0SDMZwY_ta", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3600, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Viswanathan Arunaiappan", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/109714187210279255847", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUWM9MwQeZQRolAXTb0RuZveLEZTDH6uhNSF0YcH3fBChSdAPO=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhDVJpMPnxVMViULA4p5gUQd&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIABIhDVJpMPnxVMViULA4p5gUQd!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x808f93ddb8784775:0x1083a89500586d87"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdUd4uN2Tj4ARh21YAJWogxA/photos/AWCwydjQ8uv7GK0xIvbh9m6mWE5xGHvVWTzk9ObOU-iJNz_fIPnIAAQbqmgwNySnDhEvTq8AtZ7CBwcHmjacwG9o7l